works.description: This has to be one of the most beautiful kayaks I’ve ever come across. The Cedar Strip wooden kayak from Justin Charles is made from a composite of Western red cedar strips and glass fiber. The lightweight, handcrafted kayak weighs a mere 38lbs and features watertight storage compartments, adjustable foot braces, seat and backrest, carrying handles and deck rigging included. The kayak is available in a 18′ 4″ model with a 21″ beam. Whether you’re exploring or just on a quick ride, this wooden kayak lets you enjoy the freedom and fun of kayaking
